'''桶裝炸彈'''，或譯'''桶炸彈'''、'''油桶炸彈'''（{{lang-en|Barrel bomb}}），是指一種簡易形式的[[非導引炸彈|非導引炸彈]]，或稱飛行式IED（[[簡易爆炸裝置|簡易爆炸裝置]]），屬於[[土製炸彈|土製炸彈]]的一種。這種炸彈通常裝在大型的[[油桶|油桶]]或桶狀的[[金屬|金屬]]容器，內有高爆[[炸藥|炸藥]]、[[榴霰彈|榴霰彈]]、[[油|油]]或[[化學武器|化學武器]]，使用[[飛機|飛機]]或[[直升機|直升機]]投擲落下後爆炸<ref>{{cite web |last=McElroy |first=Damien |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9512719/Syrian-regime-deploys-deadly-new-weapons-on-rebels.html |title=Syrian regime deploys deadly new weapons on rebels |publisher=Telegraph |date= |accessdate=2013-11-30 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104121124/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9512719/Syrian-regime-deploys-deadly-new-weapons-on-rebels.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於這種炸彈使用了大量炸藥，但[[精度|精度]]相當差，且又被濫用於包括[[難民營|難民營]]在內的人口群居處，其所產生的爆炸是毀滅性的<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/syrias-deadly-barrel-bombs-20120901-2573t.html |title=Syria's deadly barrel bombs |accessdate=2015-05-30 |archive-date=2019-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504033828/https://www.smh.com.au/world/syrias-deadly-barrel-bombs-20120901-2573t.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9512719/Syrian-regime-deploys-deadly-new-weapons-on-rebels.html|title=Syrian regime deploys deadly new weapons on rebels|date=31 August 2012|work=Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=13 November 2014|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510100404/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9512719/Syrian-regime-deploys-deadly-new-weapons-on-rebels.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zg5UEz_Ao0g|title=A City Left in Ruins: The Battle for Aleppo|publisher=Vice News|accessdate=2015-05-30|archive-date=2020-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307204812/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zg5UEz_Ao0g|dead-url=no}}</ref>。批評者認為此種炸彈的特性等同恐怖武器，且根據國際公約，使用這種炸彈是違法的<ref name=bbc>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25466541 |title=Barrel bombs show brutality of war |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |author=Jonathan Marcus |date=December 20, 2013 |accessdate=May 20, 2015 |quote=..the campaigning group Human Rights Watch has insisted that the employment of these weapons constitutes a war crime and that those responsible should be held to account. |archive-date=2015-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428135055/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25466541 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

目前已知最早使用桶裝炸彈的歷史是始於以色列軍隊，<ref>{{cite journal |title=Mahal and the Dispossession of the Palestinians |journal=[[Journal_of_Palestine_Studies|Journal of Palestine Studies]] |author1=Dan Freeman-maloy |date=Winter 2011 |volume=40 |number=2 |url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/10.1525/jps.2011.XL.2.43 |accessdate=June 29, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305080557/https://www.jstor.org/stable/10.1525/jps.2011.XL.2.43 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url= |title=The Palestinian Exodus from Galilee, 1948'' |publisher=[[Institute_for_Palestine_Studies|Institute for Palestine Studies]] |author=Nafez Nazzal |year=1978 |page=75 |accessdate=June 29, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.qq.com/a/20160309/029834.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-27 |archive-date=2016-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328051025/http://news.qq.com/a/20160309/029834.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
第二個已知使用桶裝炸彈是美軍在越南在60年代末期。<ref name=tharoor>{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/02/16/when-the-u-s-dropped-barrel-bombs-in-war/ |title=When the U.S. dropped barrel bombs in war |work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]] |author=Ishaan Tharoor |date=February 16, 2015 |accessdate=February 17, 2015 |archive-date=2015-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509054927/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/02/16/when-the-u-s-dropped-barrel-bombs-in-war/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/02/16/when-the-u-s-dropped-barrel-bombs-in-war/ |title=When the U.S. dropped barrel bombs in war |work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]] |author=Ishaan Tharoor |date=February 16, 2015 |accessdate=October 11, 2015 |archive-date=2015-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509054927/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/worldviews/wp/2015/02/16/when-the-u-s-dropped-barrel-bombs-in-war/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
20世紀90年代開始，他們也被用於在斯里蘭卡，克羅地亞和蘇丹。1991年的[[克羅埃西亞戰爭|克罗地亚]]，他們將炸彈安置於[[安-2|安-2]]農用飛機，用以對付在[[武科瓦尔|武科瓦尔]]周圍的[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]人陣地；而90年代期間，[[苏丹共和国|苏丹共和国]]也使用過這種炸彈，當時被裝載於貨艙[[運輸機|運輸機]]中再拋出；最常使用的此種炸彈的是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中的[[敘利亞空軍|敘利亞空軍]]，另外在[[安巴爾衝突|安巴爾衝突]]中的伊拉克軍隊也有使用。軍事專家們認為，由於這種炸彈價格低廉，容易大量製造，在內有叛亂武裝分子的國家，桶裝炸彈仍會被繼續被具有空中優勢的政府軍使用於戰爭中<ref name=jakes>{{cite web |url=https://news.yahoo.com/barrel-bombs-risk-becoming-answer-insurgency-073510814.html |title=Barrel bombs risk becoming answer to insurgency |work=Yahoo News |agency=Associated Press |author=Lara Jakes |date=May 7, 2014 |accessdate=June 7, 2014 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717040007/https://news.yahoo.com/barrel-bombs-risk-becoming-answer-insurgency-073510814.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
桶裝炸彈的製造成本相當低廉，每桶炸彈的[[成本|成本]]只需200至300[[美元|美元]]間<ref name=dechett>{{cite web |url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/07/03/built_it_yourself_bombs_barrel_bombs_syria_sudan |title=The Build-It-Yourself Bombs |work=Foreign Policy |author=Torie Rose DeGhett |date=July 3, 2014 |accessdate=July 14, 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825073710/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2014/07/03/built_it_yourself_bombs_barrel_bombs_syria_sudan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它可以被掛載在任何類型的軍用飛機上，也包括非軍用的運輸機。桶裝炸彈的爆炸載荷（explosive payload）可以採用非常簡單的原料，例如{{link-en|肥料炸彈|ANFO}}（[[硝酸铵|硝酸铵]]與[[燃油|燃油]]混合）。炸彈內可能含有金屬彈片，如[[螺母|螺母]]或[[螺栓|螺栓]]，甚至可能含有化學品[[氯|氯]]<ref name=moses-chemical>[http://brown-moses.blogspot.com.au/2014/04/evidence-chlorine-gas-was-used-in-kafr.html Evidence Chlorine Gas Was Used In The Kafr Zita Chemical Attack] {{Wayback|url=http://brown-moses.blogspot.com.au/2014/04/evidence-chlorine-gas-was-used-in-kafr.html |date=20140413222911 }}, brown-moses.blogspot.com.au.</ref>。炸彈被裝在使用簡易材料製成，專為炸彈設計的桶狀容器內<ref name=moses1222>{{cite web |url=http://brown-moses.blogspot.com/2013/12/syrias-barrel-bomb-technology-relative.html |title=Syria's Barrel Bomb Technology Relative To Aleppo Syria Attacks - The Good, The Bad And The Ugly |work=Brown Moses Blog |author=[[Brown_Moses|Brown Moses]] |date=December 22, 2013 |accessdate=April 1, 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328012631/http://brown-moses.blogspot.com/2013/12/syrias-barrel-bomb-technology-relative.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]所使用的早期版本還有需點燃的[[引信|引信]]，所以必須小心計時，否則可能過早或過晚爆炸<ref name=moses1222>{{cite web |url=http://brown-moses.blogspot.com/2013/12/syrias-barrel-bomb-technology-relative.html |title=Syria's Barrel Bomb Technology Relative To Aleppo Syria Attacks - The Good, The Bad And The Ugly  |work=Brown Moses Blog |author=[[Brown_Moses|Brown Moses]] |date=December 22, 2013 |accessdate=April 1, 2015}}</ref> ；不過隨著時間推移，對炸彈也做了修正與改進，現在已有了碰炸引信（Impact fuse）與穩定尾翼（stabilizing fin）<ref name=moses1222>{{cite web |url=http://brown-moses.blogspot.com/2013/12/syrias-barrel-bomb-technology-relative.html |title=Syria's Barrel Bomb Technology Relative To Aleppo Syria Attacks - The Good, The Bad And The Ugly  |work=Brown Moses Blog |author=[[Brown_Moses|Brown Moses]] |date=December 22, 2013 |accessdate=April 1, 2015}}</ref> 。早期的炸彈被限制在（100-300磅/ 45-150公斤）以內；而現在的範圍已增至1,000磅（454公斤）至1[[噸|噸]]間<ref name=dechett/>。

